  "imageAlt": "HeroQuest Rise of the Dread Moon Box",
  "description": [
    {
      "paragraph": "HeroQuest Rise of the Dread Moon is an expansion for the classic board game HeroQuest. This expansion introduces new adventures and more monsters to the original game. The dramatic story of treachery and unrest in the elven kingdom continues in this HeroQuest Rise of the Dread Moon expansion! As a brave knight, you’re challenged to finally free Elethorn from the clutches of Zargon. Embark on dangerous quests, as you seek the aid of the Cadre of the Raven's Veil to help stop Zargon's forces of Dread from destroying the kingdom. Navigate through a dark labyrinth of waterways, an underground city, and more perilous locations. But be wary—for Zargon's forces grow ever stronger with the rise of the Dread Moon!"
    },
    {
      "paragraph": "The expansion includes 10 new quests and additional miniatures. Players can take on the role of a Knight."
    },
    {
      "paragraph": "This expansion is designed to be used in conjunction with the original HeroQuest game, and players will need the core box to fully enjoy the new content and features introduced in \"HeroQuest Rise of the Dread Moon.\""
    }
  ],
